# <type>: <imperative summary, <=72 chars>
#
# Body (wrap at 72): explain WHY the change is needed and its user-visible
# effect. Skip the "what" when the diff is self-explanatory.
#
# type: feat | fix | docs | refactor | test | chore | perf | ci
#
# This template is opt-in per clone — enable it once with:
#   git config commit.template .gitmessage
